eferred) Solid knowledge of accounting principles and practices (GAAP, IFRS a plus) Hands-on experience using Microsoft office products including MS Excel, PowerPoint and Words, SAP a plus Ability to work independently and collaboratively in an entrepreneurial start-up like environment ", 
